      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REFEMME NO ANGEL (5) is on resumption today after ending last campaign with a solid performance in Saturday company. His two trials coming into this have been solid and Pike takes the ride first-up in a good push for his chances. Can return with a bang. COSMIC TREAT (7) ended last campaign on a winning note at Pinjarra and looks to have gone to another level this time in work. She's won both 400m heats coming into this and CJP hopping on board is a good push to her chances. Drawn ideally and can pick up from where she left off. BRAVE WASP (1) was only 1.2L off the winner two back before closing nicely on the Scarpside at Pinjarra recently. A better draw this time can see him sit closer today and the blinkers are reapplied. Can bounce back to his best. DANCE ON SON (2) pulled up with an issue last start and is obviously better than that. Expecting a better effort this time. FLASH DANCER (3) can improve quickly with the fresh run under his belt.",
